subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson, a six-time Nascar Sprint Cup Series champion, won the Quicken Loans 400, his first victory in 25 Cup starts at the speedway in Brooklyn, Mich.
